title: FULL VERSION OF SUPERTRAINS 8.0 FOR ANDROID - CRACKED AND WORKIN
description:
Whats new in this version:

Four new extra levels! 
No Ads ! 
Featuring bug fixes and superior gameplay!. 
Improved audio and graphics! 
New sounds and effects!



Drive the SuperTrain around the traintracks, collecting fiery orbiters and avoiding crashing into the Red Trains! 
Control the path of the SuperTrain by touching the junction point button to switch their direction, and by adjusting the speed slider forwards and backwards. 
Don't crash into a incorrectly switched junction point, and don't drive into one of the Red Trains!. 
Collect 5 fiery orbiters and progress your way through the levels. 
Whenever you clear four levels it will open up another four levels for you to play. 
Each level gets more and more complex and difficult. 
The camera can be switched to the train drivers view and moved around by touch. 

The controls are very simple to operate, the game is very simple to play, but it is quite a challenge to master it. 


VIRUS-FREE, TROJAN-FREE, NO SPYWARE, SIMPLY WORKS!
